What you need to know:

Supply of ordinary bread now becomes vatable – 16 per cent.  Excise duty paid per motorbike from the current Sh11,608.23 per unit to a flat rate of 15 per cent. This will see any motorbike priced above Sh79,000 cost more Imported jewellery to attract excise duty at the rate of 10 per centProducts containing nicotine or nicotine substitutes will attract a Sh5,000 tax per kg.